n","0261c1a4-6f2d-4135-98d2-92cb08258098",{"text":1834,"url":1835,"id":2175,"parent":2167,"weight":84},"5760a220-094a-4ccb-b66b-1233a7b2227c",{"text":1838,"url":1839,"id":2177,"parent":2167,"weight":89},"f42746f6-de2e-4012-a0c9-bf2fa5e082e8",{"text":1808,"url":1809,"id":2179,"parent":6,"weight":2015,"items":2180},"8e27bd9c-2bc0-42ef-9ff3-75c6b3226f5f",[2181,2183],{"text":1813,"url":1814,"id":2182,"parent":2179,"weight":1945},"851bf67e-a3c4-4dad-82bd-1c6db1624200",{"text":1817,"url":1818,"id":2184,"parent":2179,"weight":1948},"2df2d35b-f1dc-4a8b-a457-4b88ce125ea7",{"text":1842,"url":1843,"id":2186,"parent":6,"weight":2107},"34c51e7b-0e42-44a1-bafd-21db9728c464","published",[2189,2191],{"text":1645,"url":2190},"/topic/structure",{"text":1460,"url":2192},"/tag/about-victoria-police",[2194],{"text":1460,"url":2192},{"text":1645,"url":2190},{"title":1747,"summary":2197,"links":2198,"backgroundImageCaption":8,"theme":2200,"logoImage":6,"backgroundImage":6,"cornerTop":6,"cornerBottom":6,"primaryAction":6,"secondaryAction":6,"secondaryActionLabel":8},"At Victoria Police, we are proud to serve our community through dedicated staff, comprehensive services, and a steadfast commitment to safety, wellbeing, and our core values.",{"title":8,"items":2199,"more":6},[],"default",{"id":2202,"name":1943,"siteOverrides":2203},548,{"showQuickExit":6,"featureFlags":2204},{},{"url":1748,"langcode":2206,"description":2197,"additional":2207,"keywords":8,"image":6},"en",[2208,2213,2217,2222],{"tag":2209,"attributes":2210},"meta",{"name":2211,"content":2212},"title","Our people, services, and commitment | Victoria Police",{"tag":2209,"attributes":2214},{"name":2215,"content":2216},"description","Learn about Victoria Police's values, our staff, services, mission and role, commitment to safety and the community, and our Victoria Police regions.",{"tag":2218,"attributes":2219},"link",{"rel":2220,"href":2221},"canonical","https://content.police.vic.gov.au/our-people-services-and-commitment",{"tag":2209,"attributes":2223},{"property":2224,"content":2225},"og:locale","en-AU","Our people, services, and commitment to the Victorian community.","h2",[],[2230,2245,2289,2307,2316,2332,2341],{"uuid":2231,"component":2232,"id":2233,"internalAnchors":2234,"props":2243},"5a79be2c-8ecf-4e14-bace-87b3045b072a","TideLandingPageContent","17026",[2235,2238,2240],{"text":2236,"id":2237,"type":2227},"Our staff","our-staff",{"text":1037,"id":2239,"type":2227},"our-services",{"text":2241,"id":2242,"type":2227},"Our mission and role","our-mission-and-role",{"html":2244},"\u003Cp>Victoria Police was established in 1853 and provides policing services to the Victorian community 24 hours a day.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>We work every day to keep all Victorians safe.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2 id=\"our-staff\">Our staff\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>Victoria Police employees are made up of:\u003C/p>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>police officers\u003C/li>\u003Cli>protective services officers (PSOs)\u003C/li>\u003Cli>police custody officers (PCOs) and\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Victorian Public Service (VPS) employees.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003Cp>Police officers, PSOs and PCOs are supported in their roles by public service professionals. VPS employees drive and support the strategic initiatives of the organisation. They work in a range of functions such as legal services, accounting, psychology and forensic sciences.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Our workforce is continuously expanding with new recruits every year.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2 id=\"our-services\">Our services\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>Victoria Police operates under the \u003Ca href=\"https://www.legislation.vic.gov.au/in-force/acts/victoria-police-act-2013/045\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">\u003Cspan>Victoria Police Act 2013\u003C/span>\u003C/a>. Our services include:\u003C/p>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>responding to calls for assistance in matters of personal and public safety, emergencies, and serious incidents\u003C/li>\u003Cli>preventing crime through a range of \u003Ca href=\"/programs-and-initiatives\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"340ff9fd-6429-477e-8f56-87bb7951b8bc\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Programs and initiatives\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">proactive community safety programs\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>detecting and investigating offences and bringing to justice those responsible for committing them\u003C/li>\u003Cli>providing a visible presence within the community and at major events\u003C/li>\u003Cli>supporting the judicial process to achieve efficient and effective court case management, providing safe custody for alleged offenders, supporting victims, and ensuring fair and equitable treatment of victims and offenders\u003C/li>\u003Cli>providing professional \u003Ca href=\"/police-prosecutions\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"19a8a0da-4cf6-442b-979c-6a25f8878bbc\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Police prosecutions\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">prosecution services\u003C/a> to support judicial proceedings\u003C/li>\u003Cli>assisting coroners with their investigations into deaths and fires, and support to our members who are investigating matters on behalf of coroners\u003C/li>\u003Cli>managing and coordinating major \u003Ca href=\"/emergency-response\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"437b2e50-3555-4bbc-8bbb-7741318c402d\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Emergency response\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">emergency responses\u003C/a> with other agencies\u003C/li>\u003Cli>promoting \u003Ca href=\"/road-safety\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"bac33ae4-99ae-43d7-af17-d69aff4c6555\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Road safety\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">safe road-user behaviour\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>conducting \u003Ca href=\"/private-security\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"3b2ee104-054c-475b-86eb-a878096b5b66\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Private security\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">private security\u003C/a> and \u003Ca href=\"/firearms-licensing\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"c6f94bfd-020a-41f4-988f-3058cc44945c\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Firearms licensing\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">firearms licensing\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>conducting \u003Ca href=\"/national-police-records-checks\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"28247f4b-c755-425f-a308-80449ea45b46\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"National police checks and fingerprinting\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">national police record and fingerprint checks\u003C/a>.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003Cp>To explore detailed information, visit \u003Ca href=\"/our-services\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"e3e3de2e-53b4-4efc-af25-f9beb4947d89\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Our services\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">Our services page\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2 id=\"our-mission-and-role\">Our mission and role\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>Our mission is for everyone to be safe and feel safe.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Our role is to serve the Victorian community and uphold the law to promote a safe, secure, and orderly society.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>We achieve this by:\u003C/p>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>preserving the peace\u003C/li>\u003Cli>protecting life and property\u003C/li>\u003Cli>preventing offences\u003C/li>\u003Cli>detecting and apprehending offenders\u003C/li>\u003Cli>helping those in need of assistance\u003C/li>\u003Cli>working with \u003Ca href=\"https://www.police.vic.gov.au/our-community\" title=\"Community partners and reference groups\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">local communities, partners and reference groups\u003C/a>.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"uuid":2246,"component":2247,"id":2248,"title":2249,"props":2250},"f383e3e7-8c0f-4708-94b6-c0edaf3d8029","TideLandingPageTimeline","18126","Our values",{"items":2251},[2252,2261,2268,2275,2282],{"id":2253,"title":2254,"subtitle":6,"url":8,"description":2255,"image":2256,"current":1927,"dateStart":6,"dateEnd":6},"18121","Compassion","\u003Ch5>We act with compassion through tolerance, understanding and impartiality.\u003C/h5>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>Have respect for difference through inclusiveness and open-mindedness.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Build positive relationships with the community and our colleagues through empathy and active listening.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Prioritise crime prevention and the needs of victims.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Act with genuine kindness, empathy and understanding of the diverse needs of the community.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"src":2257,"alt":8,"title":8,"width":2258,"height":2258,"focalPoint":2259},"/sites/default/files/2025-08/About-us-A-Safe-Victoria-Digital-publication-Compassion-blue-icon.png",417,{"x":2260,"y":2260},209,{"id":2262,"title":2263,"subtitle":6,"url":8,"description":2264,"image":2265,"current":1927,"dateStart":6,"dateEnd":6},"18122","Respect","\u003Ch5>We treat everyone fairly, with dignity and respect; they are valued and included.\u003C/h5>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>Treat each other and every community member with respect and understanding.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Celebrate and value equity, diversity and inclusion.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Value the unique place of Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander peoples, as First Nations people, and their rich history and culture, along with the diverse backgrounds of other community members.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"src":2266,"alt":8,"title":8,"width":2258,"height":2258,"focalPoint":2267},"/sites/default/files/2025-08/About-us-A-Safe-Victoria-Digital-publication-Respect-blue-icon.png",{"x":2260,"y":2260},{"id":2269,"title":2270,"subtitle":6,"url":8,"description":2271,"image":2272,"current":1927,"dateStart":6,"dateEnd":6},"18123","Integrity","\u003Ch5>We act with integrity and honour, being fair and respectful of both the law and human rights.\u003C/h5>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>Be honest, objective and impartial.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Respect and champion human rights and commit to lawful and fair processes.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Place the good of the community before our own interests.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Build the trust and confidence of the community.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"src":2273,"alt":8,"title":8,"width":2258,"height":2258,"focalPoint":2274},"/sites/default/files/2025-08/About-us-A-Safe-Victoria-Digital-publication-Integrity-blue-icon.png",{"x":2260,"y":2260},{"id":2276,"title":2277,"subtitle":6,"url":8,"description":2278,"image":2279,"current":1927,"dateStart":6,"dateEnd":6},"18124","Professionalism","\u003Ch5>We are accountable and professional; committed to maintaining the highest standards of conduct and presentation.\u003C/h5>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>Behave in a manner that reflects positively on ourselves and our organisation.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Perform our duties with care and skill, provide services that are engaging, accessible and equitable.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Take pride in the way we look and act.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Be open, adaptable and resilient, and value collaboration and teamwork.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"src":2280,"alt":8,"title":8,"width":2258,"height":2258,"focalPoint":2281},"/sites/default/files/2025-08/About-us-A-Safe-Victoria-Digital-publication-Professionalism-blue-icon.png",{"x":2260,"y":2260},{"id":2283,"title":2284,"subtitle":6,"url":8,"description":2285,"image":2286,"current":1927,"dateStart":6,"dateEnd":6},"18125","Courage","\u003Ch5>We act with courage and uphold the values in the face of adversity.\u003C/h5>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>Make robust and ethical decisions in challenging circumstances.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Challenge inappropriate behaviours and encourage others to do the same.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Show humility and strength of character.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Be innovative.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"src":2287,"alt":8,"title":8,"width":2258,"height":2258,"focalPoint":2288},"/sites/default/files/2025-08/About-us-A-Safe-Victoria-Digital-publication-Courage-blue-icon.png",{"x":2260,"y":2260},{"uuid":2290,"component":2232,"id":2291,"internalAnchors":2292,"props":2305},"994b17d8-1630-4456-9684-fc62305620d7","17039",[2293,2296,2299,2302],{"text":2294,"id":2295,"type":2227},"Our commitment to health, safety and wellbeing","our-commitment-to-health-safety-and-wellbeing",{"text":2297,"id":2298,"type":2227},"Victoria Police regions","victoria-police-regions",{"text":2300,"id":2301,"type":2227},"Victoria Police Annual Reports","victoria-police-annual-reports",{"text":2303,"id":2304,"type":2227},"Careers with Victoria Police","careers-with-victoria-police",{"html":2306},"\u003Cp>Learn more about \u003Ca href=\"/safe-victoria/safe-victoria-values\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"6c20cfab-fcec-4a5a-961f-4eb9945a072b\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"A Safe Victoria: Our values\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">our values.\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\u003Ch2 id=\"our-commitment-to-health-safety-and-wellbeing\">Our commitment to health, safety and wellbeing\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>Our role is to create a safe Victoria. To achieve this, we must:\u003C/p>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>ensure the health, safety and wellbeing of our people\u003C/li>\u003Cli>create safe and respectful workplaces.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003Cp>This requires a strong safety culture. All employees share the responsibility for workplace health, safety and wellbeing. They must commit to safe and healthy workplace practices and behaviours.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>Our commitment to health, safety and wellbeing is enhanced through the following priorities:\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>Access to a variety of internal wellbeing support services. Our Employee Assistance Program provides independent and confidential counselling services for employees and their immediate families.\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>The development of \u003C/span>\u003Ca href=\"/equal-safe-and-strong-victoria-police-gender-equality-action-plan-2022-2024\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"b7303a4c-5467-4d49-a910-0860923f2062\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Equal, Safe and Strong: Victoria Police Gender Equality Action Plan 2022-2024\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">\u003Cspan>Equal, Safe and Strong: Gender Equality Strategy 2030-2030\u003C/span>\u003C/a>\u003Cspan> and \u003C/span>\u003Ca href=\"/victoria-police-workforce-diversity-and-inclusion-framework-2023-2030\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"64d8bfc7-9487-4042-bccc-893728c884a9\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Victoria Police Workforce Diversity and Inclusion Framework 2023-2030\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">\u003Cspan>Workforce Diversity and Inclusion Framework 2023-2030\u003C/span>\u003C/a>\u003Cspan>.\u003C/span>\u003Cem>\u003Cspan> \u003C/span>\u003C/em>\u003Cspan>These strategies detail how we will ensure that all employees work in a safe and inclusive environment, where they are treated with dignity, respect and fairness.\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003Ch2 id=\"victoria-police-regions\">Victoria Police regions\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>Victoria Police serves the Victorian community across four regions. These are North West Metro, Southern Metro, Eastern and Western.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>The four regions are shown on the map below.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003Cdiv class=\"rpl-media-embed rpl-media-embed--background\">\n        \u003Cfigure class=\"rpl-media-embed__main--contain\">\n          \u003Cimg src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-09/Victoria-Police-regions.PNG\" class=\"rpl-image\" width=\"893\" height=\"649\" alt=\"Victoria Police divisional regions, North West Metro region, Southern Metro region, Eastern region and Western region. \" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/2024-09/Victoria-Police-regions.PNG?width=720, /sites/default/files/2024-09/Victoria-Police-regions.PNG?width=1440 2x\">\n        \u003C/figure>\n      \u003C/div>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"victoria-police-annual-reports\">Victoria Police Annual Reports\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>Read our latest \u003Ca href=\"/annual-report\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"29e793a8-da1c-4a44-9ec3-32e7d7ba5f03\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" title=\"Annual reports\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">Annual Report\u003C/a> for \u003Cspan>a record of our achievements and significant activities undertaken through the year.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003Ch2 id=\"careers-with-victoria-police\">Careers with Victoria Police\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>We are looking for the right people who want to make a difference every day. Become part of a dynamic organisation, dedicated to making Victoria a safe place to work and live.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003Cp>\u003Cspan>Take the first step in your exciting new career and, \u003C/span>\u003Ca href=\"https://www.police.vic.gov.au/careers\" title=\"Careers\" class=\"rpl-text-link rpl-u-focusable-inline\">\u003Cspan>learn more about Victoria Police careers\u003C/span>\u003C/a>\u003Cspan>.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>",{"uuid":2308,"component":2232,"id":2309,"internalAnchors":2310,"props":2314},"bde1a40b-9bc0-4b68-a6a8-8a8c5592b8ca","18128",[2311],{"text":2312,"id":2313,"type":2227},"Our current strategy","our-current-strategy",{"html":2315},"\u003Ch2 id=\"our-current-strategy\">Our current strategy\u003C/h2>",{"uuid":2317,"component":2318,"id":2319,"props":2320},"450db47b-a7a5-4e5a-a548-6cd9c549aa7f","TideLandingPageNavCard","18127",{"displayStyle":2321,"title":1517,"summary":2322,"image":2323,"url":1518,"showMetadata":1927,"metadata":2330},"noImage","A Safe Victoria - where everyone is safe and feels safe, sets out our current strategy, values, and community first operating model.",{"src":2324,"focalPoint":2325,"alt":8,"width":2328,"height":2329,"title":8},"/sites/default/files/2025-08/About-us-A-Safe-Victoria-Officer-Digital-publication-1280-px-Feature-image.jpg",{"x":2326,"y":2327},640,580,1280,1159,{"dateStart":8,"dateEnd":8,"topic":1460,"contentType":2331,"fvRecommendationStatus":8,"inductionYear":8,"isGrantOngoing":1927},"Publication",{"uuid":2333,"component":2232,"id":2334,"internalAnchors":2335,"props":2339},"5b6b9c0e-df79-445d-8e6a-773ad576c732","18129",[2336],{"text":2337,"id":2338,"type":2227},"Our organisational structure","our-organisational-structure",{"html":2340},"\u003Ch2 id=\"our-organisational-structure\">Our organisational structure\u003C/h2>",{"uuid":2342,"component":2318,"id":2343,"props":2344},"2fe71976-ec5f-4600-abcf-ae91abe89277","17027",{"displayStyle":2321,"title":1645,"summary":2345,"image":6,"url":1646,"showMetadata":1927,"metadata":2346},"The organisational structure of Victoria Police, including our associations and networks.",{"dateStart":8,"dateEnd":8,"topic":1645,"contentType":2347,"fvRecommendationStatus":8,"inductionYear":8,"isGrantOngoing":1927},"Landing Page",["Reactive",2349],{},["Set"],["ShallowReactive",2352],{"site-4":6,"page-/our-people-services-and-commitment":6}]</script>
